comments: Bertans (SAS) makes marginal contact to the arm of Powell (DAL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Aldridge (SAS) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Finney-Smith (DAL).
The ball is last touched by Powell (DAL) prior to going out of bounds.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Spurs possession is confirmed.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with White's (SAS) body that affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Aldridge (SAS) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Aldridge (SAS) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Doncic (DAL).
Aldridge (SAS) initiates some contact with Powell (DAL) in the post but he does not dislodge him from his obtained position.
Aldridge (SAS) is in the lane for more than three seconds.
Mills (SAS) makes contact with Doncic's (DAL) arm as he gathers the rebound.
LAR shows White (SAS) is standing inside the three-point arc prior to the release of the free throw.
Powell (DAL) commits a take foul on Aldridge (SAS).
White (SAS) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
